        rdfs:comment      "Exoc2 = 2410030I24Rik, Sec5, Sec5l1\n" , "Exoc7 = Exo70, sec70\n" , "Exoc5tm1c(KOMP)Mbp (MGI:5774863) + Tg(Cdh16-cre)91Igr (MGI:2665300)" , "Exoc4 = Sec8" , "Arl13btm1Tc (conditional; MGI:4948239) & Tg(Nes-cre)1Kln (MGI:2176173)" , "J:234047" , "GTP-dependent binding showed partly with co-IPs from mouse IMDC3 cells, but informed by additional work with purified murine Arl13b and rat exocyst subunits showing that direct interactions are between Arl13b and each of Exoc4 and Exoc2 (didn't feel like fiddling with cross-species binding annotations)" ;
